Project Description
Illustrates a fix for working with the ASAP.NET Wizard control with VS2010 RC1


This is a very simple project implementing a Microsoft Walkthrough at http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/library/wdb4eb30%28VS.100%29.aspx and the manual patch required to get the project to compile. This fix was documented at [url:http://blogs.msdn.com/webdevtools/archive/2010/02/18/workaround-missing-declarations-for-controls-in-designer-file.aspx
